MEMBERS OF THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY

11. Compensation (Repealed)

13. Officers and Leaders (Repealed)

COMPENSATION

2005 Repeal Note.Chapter 11 (§§ 1101 - 1107) was added July 7, 2005, P.L.201, No.44, and repealed November 16, 2005, P.L.385, No.72, effective immediately. Similar subject matter is now contained in the act of September 30, 1983, P.L.160, No.39, known as the Public Official Compensation Law.
